(402, 1, '2014-11-26 11:48:44', '2014-11-26 00:48:44', 'Buying an investment property is a big step, but it doesn’t have to be a difficult one. Our EasyPlan Mortgage Advisors do all the heavy lifting so you can just sit back and enjoy the benefits.\r\n\r\nOur EasyPlan Mortgage Advisors will sit down with you so that they fully understand your goals and needs. Then they will compare hundreds of potential loans to find the best options to suit you, give you clear comparisons between loan options, explain any costs involved and, ultimately, find the right investment loan for you.\r\n\r\nThey will advise as to how much you can borrow, as well as calculating your possible monthly repayments so that you have a clear understanding of your budget when you start looking for an investment property.\r\n\r\nOnce you’ve decided on a loan, your EasyPlan Mortgage Advisor will negotiate with the lenders to get you the best possible deal. They’ll prepare all necessary paperwork and lodge your application. EasyPlan handles all the legwork involved and you don’t have to worry about a thing.\r\n\r\nMost importantly, your EasyPlan Mortgage Advisor will be there throughout the entire process so you’re never left in the dark if you have any questions.\r\n\r\n[button color="blue" title="Enquire Now" url="http://easyplan.com.au/investors/investors-enquiry/"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h6>This website only contains general information. It does not contain financial advice, and does not take into account your objectives, circumstances, or needs.\r\nYou should obtain your own financial, taxation and legal advice before making any decision. Terms, conditions, and fees may apply, along with credit assessment criteria for loan products.\r\nMembers and representatives of the ParkTrent group may receive commissions in relation to the services they provide to you, or on your behalf.\r\nPark Trent Properties Group Pty Ltd ABN 89 101 491 507 Easy Plan Financial Services Pty Ltd ABN 62 087 763 193 Australian Credit Licence 387430, Authorised Representative Number 270479 of Millennium3 Financial Services Pty Ltd AFSL Number 244252</h6>', 'What We can do for You!', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'what-easyplan-can-do-for-you', '', '', '2014-12-10 13:57:06', '2014-12-10 02:57:06', '', 7, 'http://easyplan.com.au/?page_id=402', 7, 'page', '', 0),
(403, 1, '2014-11-26 11:47:50', '2014-11-26 00:47:50', '<h1>Why Choose EasyPlan?</h1>\r\nWhether you’re purchasing a property for investment, upgrading to your next home or you’re self-employed, EasyPlan Financial Services can help you no matter what your financial needs are.\r\n\r\nOur mortgage advisors will take time to:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Understand your financial goals and requirements</li>\r\n	<li>Assist you in finding the most suitable investment property or home loan</li>\r\n	<li>Simplify the process by arranging an investment property loan for you to suit your needs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWith direct links to all major banks and lending institutions, our EasyPlan mortgage advisors will also be able to assess any risk involved in the property purchase.', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '126-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-26 11:47:50', '2014-11-26 00:47:50', '', 126, 'http://easyplan.com.au/126-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
