(508, 1, '2014-11-26 15:17:01', '2014-11-26 04:17:01', 'We require the services of a fully accredited, self-motivated and experienced Mortgage Broker to operate from our office in Prahran.\r\n\r\nThe position includes a base salary with generous bonus and success fee paid monthly. If you are looking for a great place to work, enjoy working in a team environment - then we would like to hear from you!\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Excellent commission and salary structure</li>\r\n	<li>No need to source leads</li>\r\n	<li>No home visits</li>\r\n	<li>No night work</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>To become a member of our successful team, you will need to possess the following:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Experience within a mortgage broking role, particularly residential lending</li>\r\n	<li>Current accreditations with major lenders</li>\r\n	<li>Knowledge of property investment analysis software an advantage</li>\r\n	<li>Excellent time management skills and ability to handle high volumes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIn return we offer a competitive base salary and uncapped commissions with expected income of over $100K per annum easily achievable.\r\n\r\n<em>Please note only short listed candidates will be contacted and only Australian permanent residents need apply.</em>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class="box shad-blue"></div>\r\n[contact-form-7 id="501" title="Careers Enquiry"]', 'Mortgage Broker', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'mortgage-broker', '', '', '2015-01-16 09:58:15', '2015-01-15 22:58:15', '', 455, 'http://easyplan.com.au/?page_id=508', 0, 'page', '', 0),
