(836, 1, '2014-12-10 13:58:49', '2014-12-10 02:58:49', '<h3><em>Taking the vacation you have always wanted may be easier than you think. Take your mind off the finances and focus on your dream trip.</em></h3>\r\nIf you''ve been bitten by the travel bug and can''t wait for your savings to grow, a loan can be an ideal solution to supplement your travel budget. Loans can help you pay for airfares, accommodation, sightseeing tours, shopping and much more. They can also provide some peace of mind, knowing that you will have extra cash to cover any unexpected expenses that may arise. Approvals typically happen quite quickly: you''ll be packing your suitcase much sooner than you think!\r\n\r\nDon’t just chuck any extra charges on your credit card, travel loans have a much better rate and can save you a lot in the long run. As with any financing decision, it is important that you can afford the repayments and are able to meet the terms of the loan. A holiday loan gives you the freedom to jet off on your next adventure without the stress and hassle caused by finding ways to fund it. With financing sourced through EasyPlan, you''ll spend more time worrying about choosing your destination than how you are going to pay for it.\r\n\r\nWorking with an EasyPlan finance advisor means that you can travel with ease, knowing that you have secured a holiday loan that offers you the best value for money. EasyPlan''s team of professional advisors will help you find the appropriate financing option to get your holiday off to a great start. We work with leading banks and lending institutions to find our clients the right loan to suit their needs and financial situation.\r\n\r\nTaking out a loan involves many important decisions such as whether a fixed or variable rate loan is best. Any establishment or ongoing fees, payment terms and if a secured or unsecured loan is right for you are just some of the other features our team will help you to consider.\r\n\r\n[button color="blue" title="Enq